    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- NOTES -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <mxCell id="notes" value="&lt;b&gt;Notes&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Hall sensors NOT used — AS5048A absolute encoder handles commutation, velocity, and position from power-on (no calibration spin needed)&lt;br&gt;• MOSI must be connected — ODrive requires it for SPI bus to function even though AS5048A is read-only&lt;br&gt;• MISO and SCK are shared; only CS lines are per-axis (GPIO3 / GPIO4)&lt;br&gt;• ODrive config: encoder.mode = ENCODER_MODE_SPI_ABS_AMS · abs_spi_cs_gpio_pin = 3 (axis0) or 4 (axis1)&lt;br&gt;• TJA1050 outputs 5 V on RXD — add resistor divider or use SN65HVD230 (3.3 V) instead"
      style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#666666;fillColor=#f5f5f5;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingRight=8;spacingTop=8;fontSize=10;rounded=1;"
      vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="100" y="800" width="680" height="110" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

